Nelson Peltz

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Nelson Peltz


Born
(1942-06-24) June 24, 1942 (age 75)
Brooklyn, New York, U.S.


Residence
Bedford, New York
Palm Beach, Florida[1]


