Personal life[edit]




Peltz's children, Will and Nicola, at the 2014 Toronto International Film Festival


Peltz has been married three times. His third wife is Claudia Heffner, a former fashion model, with whom he has eight children. He has two children from his prior marriages.[43] Among Peltz's children are actors Nicola Peltz[44] and Will Peltz.[45] His son Brad Peltz was a professional ice hockey player who played in the ECHL during the 2012–13 ECHL season.[46]
